snippet: Phil Jackson won 11 championships as a coach but has never been a front-office executive. That could change.
abstract: New York Knicks owner James L Dolan meets with Phil Jackson, adding to speculation that Jackson might take a leadership role in the team's front office; Jackson has never held such an executive post, despite having won 11 championships as a coach.
lead_paragraph: Phil Jackson won 11 championships as a coach but has never been a front-office executive. That could change.

headline.main: Intrigue Over Jackson Continues to Percolate
headline.print_headline: Intrigue Over Jackson Continues to Percolate
